            "creation_date": 1479331901,
            "body": "<p>Why do you want to read them into different arrays?  Is that what your assignment asks for?  A better solution to this is to create an object with your properties like Employee, then add each Employee to a <code>List&lt;Employee&gt;<\/code><\/p>\n\n<p>If you're asking how to iteratively add items to your array, you need an index that starts at 0 and ends at array.length - 1.<\/p>\n",
